metric_captur...ng_path_groups(25.10)    metric_captur...ng_path_groups(25.10)

Name
       metric_capture_timing_path_groups

Syntax
        metric_capture_timing_path_groups <path_group>

       Default: The default value of this string variable is not set.

       Controls  the  path  groups  for which detailed timing path information
       (full timing path report and display) is to be captured .  By  default,
       it  is  empty and the tool captures all and reg2reg.   If the global is
       set to a list of groups, the tool will use the listed groups.  The  re-
       lated metric name is timing.setup.paths.path_group:<group>.

